# CODEOWNERS - Tool Delivery Gates Protection

# ============================================================
# Skip Gates Label Protection
# ============================================================
# Only the following users/teams can add the "skip-gates" or "hotfix" labels:
# - Repository owners
# - Maintainers team
#
# This is enforced through:
# 1. Branch protection rules (require PR reviews from code owners)
# 2. GitHub Actions workflow (check-label-author)
#
# To request skip-gates label:
# 1. Create PR
# 2. Add comment: "@maintainers please add skip-gates label with reason: <reason>"
# 3. Wait for maintainer approval
# ============================================================

# These paths require maintainer review for skip-gates label
/tools/ @moonlight
/integrations/ @moonlight
/handlers/ @moonlight
/schemas/ @moonlight
/POLICIES/ @moonlight
/.github/workflows/tool-gates.yml @moonlight

# Default owners for everything
* @moonlight
